title: 09/14/21 DPS Hour 3 Ross Tucker and Rick Neuheisel
itunes:title: 09/14/21 DPS Hour 3 Ross Tucker and Rick Neuheisel
description:
Ross Tucker says that the Raiders won the game rather than the Ravens losing. Ross says that Derek Carr is still not his choice for QB. Rick Neuheisel tells Dan that the USC timing of the firing makes no sense to him.
